summary:
Production Leader/ Maintenance Manager: 
- Lean / TQM / EFQM assessment experience in Rail way / Transportation sector:
- Management of teams (130 fte, 4 divisions )
     - Human Resource of employees 
     - Evaluation of employees
- Quality Management : ISO 9001 / ISO 14001 / OHSAS 18000 experience in application, audits, and process implementation
- KPI (KPA) Key Perfomance Indicators (development, implementation, .... )
- Facility Management 
- Maintenance Rolling Stock  (Planning, Resoursces, instalations,...) 
Technical Expert: 
- Quality management hoisting appliances 
    - ISO 17020 & ISO 17065 
    - NCR Non conformity issues and supervision and Corrective actions 
- Internal Audits / External Audits (Hoisting) with BELAC _Authority 
- Training / Qualifications / Audits of inspectors hoisting machinery
- Design review hoisting machinery ( STS Cranes, Mobile Cranes, Tower Cranes,... ) 
- Design Review PED
- Expert trainer of the Belgian Authorities regarding hoisitng appliances 
- Leading Quality Team Hoisting
- Commissioning Testing (FAT/ SAT protocols) 
-...
